               <person>
                  <persName role="owner" corresp="PRS0000">According to Additio 1 ʾabunä Gäbrä Ḥǝywät donated the Ms. (s. also donation note fol. 2r). The names in the original donation note were washed out (s. Additio 2); other persons are mentioned in supplication formulas: Wängelawit (s. fols. 84ra, 84rb, 92vb, 94va), Habtä Maryam (fol. 86vb), Mäsqäl Kǝbra (fol. 87va). Elsewhere, a few other names are crudely written, interlineally, by a different hand; Kidanä Maryam in supplication formulas (fols. 20va, 25va, 40vb, 50va, 50va, 85va); Näftalem (fols. 84vb, 86ra, 86vb, 87v-88r). Possibly, these Kidanä Maryam and Näftalem are linked to ʾabunä Gäbrä Ḥǝywät.</persName>
